V0401_01_00_00_0.text: To be the greatest, ya gotta take chances!

V0401_01_00_00_1.text: Then you must take every chance you can get, Yuma.

V0401_01_00_01_0.text: Time to high five the sky, Astral!

V0401_01_00_02_0.text: We must win this Duel, Yuma.

We will!
With you by my side, there's nothing we can't do!

V0401_01_00_03_1.text:

I sense our opponent is no ordinary foe.

V0401_01_00_04_0.text:
Duel Disk, go!
Duel Gazer, let's roll!

V0401_01_00_11_0.text:

Okaaaay!

V0401_01_00_08_0.text:
Kite!
Get set to get decked!

V0401_01_00_08_1.text: Defeating him will be a challenge, but a worthy one.

V0401_01_00_09_0.text: I know that if we Duel, we can become friends!

V0401_01_00_10_0.text:
Yuma!

V0401_01_00_10_1.text:

V0401_03_00_00_0.text:
You have the winning formula in hand.

V0401_03_00_05_0.text:
You have not lost yet, Yuma.
So do me a favor and Duel.

V0401_05_00_00_0.text:
The outcome of the Duel rests on this draw.
Do not fail.

V0401_05_00_00_1.text:

Zubaba General!

V0401_21_00_00_1.text: Do not let your guard down like you usually do, Yuma.

V0401_21_00_02_1.text: What should our next move be...

V0401_21_00_05_0.text:
No matter how bad it gets, I never give up!
I end my turn!

V0401_21_00_05_1.text:
Well said, Yuma.
But you are still in quite the predicament.

V0401_28_00_00_0.text:
See that, Astral?
My strategies were as sharp as steel!

V0401_28_00_00_1.text:
...Yuma, steel is just a metal.
It is not sharp.

V0401_28_00_01_0.text: You can get to really know someone by Dueling.

V0401_28_00_01_1.text: And when you're no longer strangers, you can become friends!

V0401_28_00_02_0.text: Me and Astral make a great team!

V0401_28_00_03_0.text:
I'll never give up!
As long as I feel the flow!

V0401_28_00_04_0.text: When I'm feelin' the flow, no one can beat me, Tori!

V0401_28_00_05_0.text:
How's that, Bronk!
That's the Dueling of a future champion!

V0401_28_00_06_0.text:
I did it!
I beat Shark!

V0401_28_00_07_0.text: When I'm on my game, I can high five the sky!

V0401_28_00_08_0.text: Trey, I promise I'll fight for you too!

V0401_28_00_09_0.text: This Number Card is a fragment of my memories.

V0401_29_00_00_0.text:
Man...
My flow was all clogged up...

V0401_29_00_01_0.text: Why did you not execute the moves I suggested?

V0401_29_00_01_1.text:
Cuz I'm the one who's Dueling!
Not you!

V0401_29_00_02_0.text: Do not tell me that you are going to give up?

V0401_29_00_02_1.text:
Nope!
Losing only makes the wins feel more special!

V0401_29_00_03_0.text: I gotta do better if I wanna feel the flow like my dad.

V0401_29_00_04_0.text: Way to high five the sky, Tori!

V0401_29_00_05_0.text:
I didn't high five the sky.
I high fived the ground.

V0401_29_00_06_0.text:
You really are awesome, Shark!
But I'll get ya next time!

V0401_29_00_07_0.text: Each Duel is bringin' me closer to your skill level!

V0401_29_00_07_1.text: I am learning that losing is nothing to be ashamed about.

V0401_33_00_01_0.text: This is how we will win!

V0401_33_00_02_0.text: Watch what we can do together!

V0401_30_00_02_0.text: If I can high five the sky, I can leap any obstacle!

V0401_34_00_00_0.text: Even if you play dirty, I never will!

V0401_34_00_01_0.text: I know you and I can become friends!

V0401_34_00_02_0.text: You gotta have a better reason for Dueling!

V0401_34_00_04_0.text: Observation #1: Your Dueling skills are less than skillful.

V0401_34_00_07_0.text: You have everything you need to win, Yuma!

V0401_34_00_08_0.text: I do not see how we can lose.

V0401_34_00_10_0.text: Can you please stop making dumb mistakes?

V0401_34_00_10_1.text: Saying "please" doesn't make it any nicer!

V0401_36_00_00_0.text: It's your turn to feel the flow!

V0401_36_00_02_0.text: I know we're in bad shape, but you can pull us outta this!

V0401_36_00_06_0.text: I know you got this, Kite!

V0401_36_00_07_0.text: Let's show 'em how awesome our teamwork is!

V0401_43_00_00_0.text: It's time to high five the sky!

V0401_43_00_00_3.text: When two souls become one, the power of ZEXAL is revealed!
